Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.50,0:10:04.90,Default_Sub,Com,0,0,0,,剩余可战斗时间 18秒02
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.90,0:10:08.50,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,原来如此 他的能源快用完了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.58,0:10:10.60,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,看他死撑那么久
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.60,0:10:15.49,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,一定会在能源用完前攻过来的 在补充能源前一定要干掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.36,0:10:21.08,Default_Sub,Rei,0,0,0,,能源存量不足 需补充新能源
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.08,0:10:24.80,Default_Sub,Rei,0,0,0,,推测可作战时间 最多14秒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.85,0:10:34.87,Default_Sub,Roberia,0,0,0,,队长 我一定要搞清楚事实 向军部报告
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.18,0:10:48.65,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,接下来我们怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.38,0:10:53.38,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,对啊 连比尔也死了 我们该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.78,0:10:55.29,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,只好回那个基地了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.29,0:10:56.73,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,可是都变成那样了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.88,0:10:58.46,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,里面都没有活人了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.46,0:10:59.73,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,里面有坚固的核设施
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.03,0:11:01.43,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,所以一定有生还者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.86,0:11:04.32,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,敌人肯定还会再回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.58,0:11:05.73,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,不要再拖时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.78,0:11:09.02,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,真的还有生还者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.19,0:11:12.38,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,里面是军事设施 一定会有的 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.90,0:11:14.48,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,辐射泄露不会有问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.78,0:11:16.88,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,太空服会保护我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.08,0:11:22.66,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,如果根据之前 他们对外发布的情报 短时间外面的辐射是不会渗透的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.13,0:11:25.16,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.40,0:11:29.34,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.69,0:11:33.77,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,不能一直这样绝望下去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.95,0:11:45.09,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,我们抱着仅存的一点希望 奔向火星基地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.24,0:11:47.19,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.88,0:12:22.84,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,太惨了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.21,0:12:24.34,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,如果真的如那人所说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.34,0:12:27.05,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,外星人真的计划丢导弹的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.15,0:12:28.75,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,这就是地球未来的样子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.75,0:12:42.14,Default_Sub,Anne,0,0,0,,我们到目前为止只知道两大国在做军备竞赛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.93,0:12:48.76,Default_Sub,Anne,0,0,0,,但结果会变怎样 大家却从没有想过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.59,0:12:53.89,Default_Sub,Anne,0,0,0,,不过 在这火星竟然看到这种景象
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.82,0:13:02.13,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,小心点 安娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.47,0:13:03.80,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,不要看下面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.40,0:13:08.88,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,下面真的就是我们的避难所吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.88,0:13:09.93,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.90,0:13:13.85,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,大卫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.24,0:13:40.33,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,请问 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.47,0:13:43.44,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,怎么了 大卫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.44,0:13:45.34,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,不要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.54,0:13:48.70,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,大家 来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.87,0:13:53.69,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,大卫 大家来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.85,0:13:59.99,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,有人在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.09,0:14:01.49,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,在的话请回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.74,0:14:03.59,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.80,0:14:05.29,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,电源已经关掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.69,0:14:07.54,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.58,0:14:08.59,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,有人在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.59,0:14:10.14,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,在的话请回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.58,0:14:13.34,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,门根本就没关啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.44,0:14:14.94,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,真的是像你说的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.42,0:14:18.23,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,这门应该有两到三层
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.38,0:14:44.93,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,这到底是...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.45,0:15:01.53,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,好不容易才到这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.62,0:15:07.09,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.09,0:15:08.42,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.47,0:15:12.61,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,令人难以置信的事实
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.41,0:15:17.47,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,本来应该是避难所的地方 现在里面全是尸体
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.62,0:15:34.11,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,运输船在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.72,0:15:39.04,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.37,0:15:43.52,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,明明叫他把人都杀了的 想逃走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.40,0:15:48.63,Default_Sub,Rei,0,0,0,,警报
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.63,0:15:51.22,Default_Sub,Rei,0,0,0,,有一架SPT朝着过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.69,0:15:53.52,Default_Sub,Roberia,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.72,0:15:55.07,Default_Sub,Roberia,0,0,0,,我有件事想确认
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.37,0:15:56.01,Default_Sub,Roberia,0,0,0,,你有听到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.10,0:16:01.93,Default_Sub,Roberia,0,0,0,,你真的没有杀嘉斯坦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.43,0:16:04.13,Default_Sub,Roberia,0,0,0,,我只想知道这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.08,0:16:10.06,Default_Sub,Roberia,0,0,0,,到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.06,0:16:10.83,Default_Sub,Roberia,0,0,0,,回答我 英二
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.37,0:16:15.06,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,这种事去问你的上司
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.46,0:16:16.86,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,我怎么可能做那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.30,0:16:18.28,Default_Sub,Roberia,0,0,0,,果然是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.97,0:16:30.31,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,我射错了 原谅我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.15,0:16:44.47,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,现在就算到运输船那里 也没法发射
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.14,0:16:46.46,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,不能再多给我一点时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.71,0:16:52.66,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,那家伙 跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.45,0:17:13.79,Default_Sub,Rei,0,0,0,,能源残存量 002单位
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.08,0:17:17.67,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,这样还能用激光枪吗 开枪的话我就完了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.22,0:17:23.09,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.64,0:17:32.87,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,你完啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.05,0:17:35.26,Default_Sub,Roberia,0,0,0,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.51,0:17:44.35,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.65,0:17:45.36,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.97,0:17:50.81,Default_Sub,Roberia,0,0,0,,队长 明明就是你杀了嘉斯坦 刚才还连我都想杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.81,0:17:52.97,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,不要挡路 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.43,0:18:04.22,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,混 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.15,0:18:11.79,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.76,0:18:19.51,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,你下不了杀手的 想杀的话就来试试看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.46,0:18:27.50,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.51,0:18:30.79,Default_Sub,Rei,0,0,0,,能源残存量 001单位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.63,0:18:34.13,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,我要把你扯碎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.14,0:18:38.06,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,把玖丽亚那悲伤的脸再一次地映在你脸上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.26,0:18:39.71,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,为什么提到姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.81,0:18:40.62,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,你到底做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.62,0:18:41.98,Default_Sub,Rei,0,0,0,,警报
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.98,0:18:43.88,Default_Sub,Rei,0,0,0,,受到强大的压力袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.81,0:19:12.10,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,不要跑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.45,0:19:18.55,Default_Sub,Roberia,0,0,0,,队长 我要把你送到军部
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.28,0:19:24.20,Default_Sub,Roberia,0,0,0,,随便把部下丢下的人 不配当我们的长官
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.20,0:19:25.62,Default_Sub,Roberia,0,0,0,,你给我待在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.62,0:19:27.09,Default_Sub,Roberia,0,0,0,,我去捉那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.46,0:19:31.50,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.14,0:19:38.80,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,{\pos(780,1010)\bord1\3c&HE5F3CB&\b0}古拉多斯三足式运输船
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.80,0:19:42.80,Default_Sub,Rei,0,0,0,,能源残存量 00单位 已到达极限
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.38,0:19:53.61,Default_Sub,Com,0,0,0,,警报
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.61,0:19:55.33,Default_Sub,Com,0,0,0,,有来自后方的追击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.20,0:19:57.98,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,{\pos(780,900)\bord1\3c&HE5F3CB&\b0}布鲁迪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.14,0:20:01.18,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.51,0:20:07.54,Default_Sub,Roberia,0,0,0,,找到你了 英二
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.88,0:20:14.22,Default_Sub,Roberia,0,0,0,,给我站起来 跟我回去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.52,0:20:17.54,Default_Sub,Roberia,0,0,0,,乖乖站在法庭上接受审判吧 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.09,0:20:26.42,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,什么军事法庭 你这笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.42,0:20:30.27,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,对你这不听命令 又藐视长官的家伙 我在这就处你死刑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.33,0:20:37.75,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,给我出来 叛徒英二
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.95,0:21:10.62,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,我才不会死在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.62,0:21:15.94,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,给我记住 我一定会回来的 我会亲手收拾你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.81,0:21:43.23,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,这样子 连最后的希望都没了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.23,0:21:48.65,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,他会回来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.85,0:21:50.65,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,不要再提那家伙的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.82,0:21:53.25,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,可是大卫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.22,0:21:57.85,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,不管怎么说 会发生这种事都跟他有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.15,0:22:01.63,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,他是来告诉我们这件事的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.83,0:22:04.19,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,我想相信他看看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.21,0:22:08.76,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,与其再争辩 不如想想今后该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.05,0:22:12.37,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,可是 只有我们的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.39,0:22:25.27,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.49,0:22:44.44,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,已经放弃的我们 在心中又亮起了希望的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.58,0:22:48.56,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,那个人回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.70,0:23:57.18,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,能出动的就快出动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.18,0:24:00.23,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,我 也是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.67,0:24:02.67,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.96,0:24:08.45,Layzner_Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs150\c&HF0E6E3&\pos(720,770)}血是红色的
